reviewText: came in faster than expected and exactly as described. i've gotten to volume 4 and i like what ive seen so far

Ignore the pervious review, this show is TOP NOTCH! unlike most US companies the japanese care about quality they make something. Perfect design, awesome case and TRUE HD quality not that upscale stuff that so many Funimation releases give. Put it this way you get what you pay for!
